nodes.text: Kinshara was a male human who served as an admiral in the Imperial Navy. Kinshara commanded the Imperial Star Destroyer Stalwart of the One Twenty-Fifth task force during the Batonn sector insurgency. Later he took part in the Battle of Denash in an attempt to stop an uprising on that planet, as well as preventing the rebel cell from joining others.
